
@{
	ViewData["Title"] = "About";
	ViewData["NavTab"] = "About";
}
<div class="py-3 about_page">
	<div class="text-center fw-bold fs-3">HLBookstore: Your Gateway to the World of Knowledge!</div>
	<div class="d-flex col-8 py-5 offset-2 justify-content-center align-items-center">
		<img class="col-5 pe-5" alt="Books" src="~/images/illustration/about_01.png" />
		<div class="fs-5">
			<div>Welcome to HLBookstore, your one-stop online destination for books of all genres.</div>
			<div class="py-4">We believe in the power of reading and strive to provide a diverse range of books that cater to all tastes. Whether you’re a fan of mystery novels, a history buff, or simply someone who enjoys losing themselves in a good book, HLBookstore has something for you.</div>
			<div>
				Our easy-to-navigate website and dedicated customer service make book shopping a breeze. Dive into the world of knowledge with HLBookstore today!
			</div>	
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="purchase_part py-5">
		<div class="text-center fw-bold fs-3 pb-4">How To Purchase Books</div>
		<div class="d-flex justify-content-around">
			<div class="col-2">
				<img class="illustration" alt="Illustration 1" src="~/images/illustration/about_02.png" />
				<div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-center">
					Browse and Select
				</div>
				<div class="fs-6">
					Navigate through our vast collection of books. Search or browse for your desired book and click on it.
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-2">
				<img class="illustration" alt="Illustration 2" src="~/images/illustration/about_03.png" />
				<div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-center">
					Add to Cart
				</div>
				<div class="fs-6">
					After reviewing the book details, click on the ‘Add to Cart’ button. This will place the book in your virtual shopping cart.
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-2">
				<img class="illustration" alt="Illustration 3" src="~/images/illustration/about_04.png" />
				<div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-center">
					Review Your Cart
				</div>
				<div class="fs-6">
					Click on the ‘Cart’ icon to review your selections. You can modify quantities or remove items.
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-2">
				<img class="illustration" alt="Illustration 4" src="~/images/illustration/about_05.png" />
				<div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-center">
					Checkout
				</div>
				<div class="fs-6">
					Proceed to checkout, enter details, select payment method, and place order.
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="fs-3 pt-5 fw-bold text-center">Our Mission</div>
	<div class="d-flex col-8 offset-2 justify-content-center align-items-center">	
		<div class="fs-5 col-7">
			<div class="pb-4">
				Our Mission at HLBookstore is to create a global community of readers by providing an extensive range of books from various genres, authors, and languages. We believe in the transformative power of reading and its ability to broaden horizons, foster empathy, and ignite curiosity.
			</div>
			<div>
				By making literature accessible and affordable, we aim to promote education and literacy, regardless of age or background. We understand that every reader is unique, and we strive to cater to these diverse tastes and preferences through our vast collection.
			</div>
		</div>
		<img class="ps-5" alt="Books" src="~/images/illustration/about_06.png" />
	</div>
</div>
